AI-Assisted SQL Injection via AInjection + Burp AI
Learning Objectives
By completing this lab, you will:

Set up and configure Burp Suite Community Edition for web application testing
Install and integrate AInjection for automated SQL injection detection
Utilize Burp Suite's built-in AI capabilities for vulnerability exploitation
Execute automated SQL injection attacks against vulnerable web applications
Analyze and interpret AI-generated attack payloads and results
